title: Narrative

* This example shows a simple table of contents using the ''tagField'' and ''level'' parameter

* The "root" elements are ''tag-like: Contents''

* The macro-call uses the ''tagField'' parameter to use a different field than tags

* The ''level'' parameter limits the displayed depth to ''2 levels''

** `ee-ee-ee` at level 3 should ''not'' be visible

{{examples-overview}}

